{
  "stem": "16106.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, she was a, a spinster.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And then there was Fraulein Gephardt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We did-- she did German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she picked me always to do the reciting of the poems.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And once I-- there was a poem, a poem about teensy little [INAUDIBLE] flowers and teensy little birdies and all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I resisted and said, I'm not, not reciting that one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was unheard of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I got expelled for three days for, from school for resisting Fraulein Gephardt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She broke into tears, poor thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had a very wonderful, a very extraordinary teacher, Professor [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Lang, ?] who did maths.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Soliviova, ?] who did, who did Russian with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Fraulein Bern-Bernais, who was our exercise teacher, whatever you call that now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But she had an affair with the rabbi, and she was German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The rabbi had affair with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He was a young rabbi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everybody knew that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fraulein Bern-Bernais.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very good at those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always got high marks in those exercises.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I was so big, probably.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], definitely, I do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were sitting in alphabetical order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody with an S sat together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] More or less.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, and then the big children sat in the back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So probably I was in the back next to, next to Hilda Saks, who was a, was a pianist and my-- a little-- little related to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she played the piano beautifully and had a big bosom at the age of 12.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And never-- I, I was so envious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cannot even tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every time she played 'The Hungarian Rhapsody' and she [INAUDIBLE] those, those chords, her bosom was swaying!",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
